OL,7,FMore than #68 million has been paid
OL,8,Fout in the past five years for
OL,9,Fchildbirth and maternity medical
OL,10,Fnegligence claims, relating to care at
OL,11,Fan NHS trust in Sussex.
OL,13,FThe University Hospitals Sussex NHS
OL,14,FFoundation Trust runs four hospitals
OL,15,Fincluding the Royal Sussex County in
OL,16,FBrighton and Worthing Hospital.
OL,18,FIt says it's made significant
OL,19,Fimprovements in recent years, so that
OL,20,Fpeople are safe in their care.
