OL,7,FAccording to NHS Resolutions the high
OL,8,Fcost usually relates to a small number
OL,9,Fof very serious incidents.
OL,11,FDr Tim Taylor, Chief of Service for
OL,12,Fthe Women and Children's Division
OL,13,Fsays: "Any occasion where a child or
OL,14,Fmother suffers harm is one too many.
OL,16,F"We understand that each of these
OL,17,Fcases are desperately difficult for
OL,18,Fthose involved and we are so sorry for
OL,19,Fanyone who experiences such distress.
